|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
|  | \|F\_{r}\|\_{2}^{2}=\sum\_{n\in\mathbb{Z}/N\mathbb{Z}}|F\_{r}(n)|^{2}=\frac{1}{r^{% 2}}\Biggl{(}1+2\sum\_{n=1}^{r-1}\Bigl{(}1-\frac{n}{r}\Bigr{)}^{2}\Biggr{)}=% \frac{1}{r^{2}}+\frac{(r-1)(2r-1)}{3r^{3}}. |  |

In particular,

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
|  | \|F\_{r}\|\_{2}^{2}\leq\frac{5}{3r}\quad\text{and hence}\quad\|F\_{r}\|\_{2}\leq% \sqrt{\frac{5}{3}}\,r^{-1/2}. |  |

###### Proof.

We compute as in the proof of Lemma 3.2:

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
|  | \|F\_{r}\|\_{2}^{2}=\sum\_{|n|\leq r-1}\frac{1}{r^{2}}\Bigl{(}1-\frac{|n|}{r}% \Bigr{)}^{2}=\frac{1}{r^{2}}\Biggl{(}1+2\sum\_{n=1}^{r-1}\Bigl{(}1-\frac{n}{r}% \Bigr{)}^{2}\Biggr{)}. |  |

Setting j=r-n, we have

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
|  | \sum\_{n=1}^{r-1}\Bigl{(}1-\frac{n}{r}\Bigr{)}^{2}=\sum\_{j=1}^{r-1}\Bigl{(}% \frac{j}{r}\Bigr{)}^{2}=\frac{1}{r^{2}}\sum\_{j=1}^{r-1}j^{2}=\frac{1}{r^{2}}% \cdot\frac{(r-1)r(2r-1)}{6}. |  |

Thus

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
|  | \|F\_{r}\|\_{2}^{2}=\frac{1}{r^{2}}+\frac{2}{r^{2}}\cdot\frac{(r-1)r(2r-1)}{6r^{% 2}}=\frac{1}{r^{2}}+\frac{(r-1)(2r-1)}{3r^{3}}. |  |

For the inequality, note that (r-1)(2r-1)\leq 2r^{2} for all r\geq 1, giving

|  |  |  |
