|  | \|F\_{r}\|\_{2}^{2}\leq\frac{1}{r^{2}}+\frac{2r^{2}}{3r^{3}}=\frac{1}{r^{2}}+% \frac{2}{3r}\leq\frac{5}{3r}, |  |

